"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"With the meteoric rise of creator opportunities in the current economy, there is now space for anyone who creates to share content, find their niche, grow a community, and eventually monetize. The best part of this all is you donâ€™t need much to even get started!\\n\\n> According to Peter Yangâ€™s [Creator Hierarchy of Needs](https://creatoreconomy.so/p/creator-hierarchy-of-needs) - The three steps for most creators are: Create, Grow and Monetize.\\n\\n### ðŸ”Steps towards becoming a Full-Time Creator\\n\\nIf you are the sort of creator who is trying to reach complete autonomy and consider creating as a full-time job, you have to chart your path there. Here is How to Go About it - \\n\\n#### ðŸŽ¬ Creating your first piece of Content\\n\\nYou might have an idea of what content you want to create but realize either the content market youâ€™re trying to break into is too saturated or your videos are just not gathering the right audience. This is why you **must** find your niche, at least in the beginning.\\n\\nFrom Peter Yangâ€™s [Creator Hierarchy of Needs](https://creatoreconomy.so/p/creator-hierarchy-of-needs) - you can think of your niche as the intersection of\\n\\n* **What interests you**\\n* **What youâ€™re good at**\\n* **What people want**\\n\\n#### **ðŸ““ Defining your Niche**\\n\\nSo how does one even start to define a niche? Think of it this way - you want to be that person who â€œThe person to DM for anything related to \\\\*\\\\*XYZ.â€ \\\\*\\\\*Double down on your strengths and narrow your focus in the beginning.\\n\\n![](https://cdn.substack.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc87edad7-141e-4cc4-8ad7-9b859d8740f0_3468x1153.jpeg)\\n\\nFor Example:\\n\\n1. Choose a category/overall brand: Lifestyle\\n2. Choose \\\\~3 subcategories/pillars: Makeup, Fashion, Skincare\\n3. Choose 1 pillar to start off with: Skincare\\n4. Your niche: Affordable Skincare Routines for Acne-prone skin\\n\\nThis niche will help you gather your first genuine audience. People want to feel seen and heard by creators, and when you carve your niche online you will gather an audience who truly connects with your content. Strive to become the expert in your niche and gain your credibility. Niche content also helps you reach that first piece of virality (for example - you can go viral for one piece of niche content and then start to grow your audience).\\n\\n#### ðŸ¤— Building your first fans - Your Audience\\n\\nIn order to build your initial fan base and even to convert your fans into super fans, you would need to create a relationship with your audience that has a few aspects of -\\n\\n![](https://cdn.substack.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6309773f-d03b-41de-9e18-fcf58d67ddd2_2163x1849.jpeg)\\n\\n* **Authenticity**: Be authentic with your fans and share real-life stories and behind the scenes on your life.\\n* **Credibility**: Build credibility by sharing any past experiences or achievements that show you are someone who is the right person to be sharing content in your vertical.\\n* **Give value**: Provide value from very early on in the form of advice, tips & tricks, e-books, videos that give value to the audience.\\n* **Be entertaining:** Add elements of humor and relatability. This can also be made easier by relating your content to the rising trends.\\n\\n> #### **ðŸ”¥ Build a brand where people love & trust you, provide a cohesive messaging & voice, provide value but entertaining at the same time.ðŸ”¥**\\n\\nðŸ‘€ This is the first part of a series of articles where weâ€™ll be sharing insights, resources, and tips & tricks on how to grow and scale as a creator. Weâ€™ll be covering things like metrics to grow as a creator, how to connect your content with trends, diversification of your brand, scaling yourself to reach full-time content creation ðŸ”¥\\n\\nAlso, join our exclusive Creator Community on Discord where we share more resources on how to grow as a creator everyday. Join [Here](https://discord.gg/m9qZhKf5)! \",\"timestamp\":1635202471,\"title\":\"Finding Your Niche as a Content Creatorâœ¨\"},\"digest\":\"WMPHi76Vz37Ohx5UTx_I6zEEyda3YNuEk_xFkyaLnvw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1D066eE871C083CE3De93A42ce70AB0549b7d5c2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"vaeP8cYt6gub1BPioJuwaHioqLrSJipg8aIGoccMVvk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ITCvh7mC2s4m71zh4GPPo7ZKouuz_H-y-3A5JNLp6JY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"G-y9NWjrygmkOTOKGyKSbnIC0-XISkwoasgjeDnVWRdAmAzjrIwFhA4VLtdMPKh8w71NaOfHDCWsZJsbBJOk4w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x004f72abe55bb6e1779876aba2a6ef5adbb78d37b74f36a89e191d805fc74ba10135d8d80a4bb762f8afc04ccfbaa88277b92080a14fae6097844874aabe312a1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"vaeP8cYt6gub1BPioJuwaHioqLrSJipg8aIGoccMVvk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ITCvh7mC2s4m71zh4GPPo7ZKouuz_H-y-3A5JNLp6JY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"WMPHi76Vz37Ohx5UTx_I6zEEyda3YNuEk_xFkyaLnvw\"}"